      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Audit Flash — New Lead\n\nWorkflow de traitement des leads Audit Flash.\n\n**Webhook URL :** POST /webhook/audit-flash-lead\n\n**Flow :**\n1. Validation payload + RGPD\n2. Brevo : chercher/creer contact\n3. Notion CONTACTS : chercher/creer\n4. Notion TRANSACTIONS : creer si pas de doublon ouvert\n5. Notion SOUMISSIONS LM : stocker donnees brutes\n6. Brevo : envoyer email rapport (template 24)\n7. J+3 : relance (template 25)\n\n**Credential requis :**\n- Brevo API Key (Header: api-key)\n- Notion Internal Integration",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 450,
        "color": 5
      },
